definitions.definition: The food and beverage a person or animal consumes.
examples: The diet of the giant panda consists mainly of bamboo.

definitions.definition: ( countable ) A controlled regimen of food and drink choices, as to gain or lose weight or otherwise influence health .
( by extension ) Any habitual intake or consumption .
examples: He's been reading a steady diet of nonfiction for the last several years.
